item.content:encoded:
Skills

  • Proficient in the use of Microsoft office suite.
  • Microsoft Excel Programming.
  • Project Management.
  • Comprehensive understanding of network architecture and client/server technology.
  • Web Development.
  • Software Development.
  • Database Management System.
  • Proficient in PHP, Java, Laravel, JavaScript, Vue, SQL, HTML 5, CSS 3 and WordPress.
  • Development and integration of API.
  • Knowledge of Scrum software development process.
  • Knowledge of Ionic.
  • Graphical and visual design skills
  • Ability to design, build and maintain e-commerce websites using various technologies.
  • Critical thinking skills to find alternative solutions to problems.
  • Exceptional skill in organizational and time management.
  • Exceptional written and verbal communication skills.
